   <concept id="FAR_34_201" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">34.201</ph> Policy.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2232e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2257e10"> 
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> In accordance with OMB Circular A-11, agencies must require an Earned Value Management System (EVMS) in major acquisitions for development. </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2257e15"> 
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> For contracts with EVMS requirements, agencies must require contractor submission of monthly EVMS reports.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2257e20"> 
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> EVMS requirements apply to subcontractors using the same rules as applied to the prime contractor. </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2257e25"> 
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> When a solicitation requires a contractor-proposed EVMS plan, agencies will determine adequacy of the plan prior to contract award.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
